PanDn
=====

Key:    `Alt+Down'
Key:    `Ctrl+Grey+'
Menu:   n/a

   Scroll the window down one line, but leave the cursor where it is.


File: tde.info,  Node: PanLeft,  Next: PanRight,  Prev: PanDn,  Up: Alphabetical List

PanLeft
=======

Key:    `Alt+Left'
Menu:   n/a

   Scroll the window left one character, but leave the cursor where it
is.


File: tde.info,  Node: PanRight,  Next: PanUp,  Prev: PanLeft,  Up: Alphabetical List

PanRight
========

Key:    `Alt+Right'
Menu:   n/a

   Scroll the window right one character, but leave the cursor where it
is.


